title: [Liquidity Pools]
body:
In order to create a strong foundation for VEST tokens, we as a community need to choose Liquidity Pools that will benefit VEST's value growth in the long term. 

VEST is created to be a multichain token, currently available on Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain, and Polygon (Matic Network). Creating the bridges to other chains will allow our DAO Invest community to adapt and thrive in the changing crypto world.

Proposal to start with 3 different Liquidity Pools:
1. Ethereum chain: Uniswap LP - ETH/VEST
2. Binance Smart Chain: PancakeSwap LP - BNB/VEST
3. Polygon: QuickSwap LP - ETH/VEST

By creating LPs on different chains our community will have a greater exposure by being in different markets and having a presence on multiple DEXs such as Uniswap, 1INCH, QuickSwap, PancakeSwap, SushiSwap, etc.
